org.reactfx.value

Interface SuspendableVar<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.beans.value.ObservableValue<T>, javafx.beans.property.Property<T>, javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyProperty<T>, Suspendable, SuspendableVal<T>, Val<T>, Var<T>, javafx.beans.value.WritableValue<T>

    public interface SuspendableVar<T>
extends SuspendableVal<T>, Var<T>
    Writable value whose invalidation and change notifications can be temporarily suspended. Multiple invalidations encountered while this observable value was suspended will result in a single invalidation and at most one change notification when resumed.
